translated: Jansson, Aron, clergyman, dean, Orslösa, b. 11/11/77 in Borås. Married 10 Nov. to Elisabet Johnsson. Children: Brita b. 14, Herbert b. 19. — Graduated from high school in Gothenburg 99, theology degree 00, theoretical theology degree in Lund 03, practical theology degree same year. Vicar in Orslösa 11, parish priest from 40. Chairman of church council in Orslösa, Söne and Väla parish meetings. Dean of Kålland district from 44. LVO award in 43.
